{"name": "genstates", "metadata": {"name": "genstates", "version": "0.1.2", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["genruler"], "summary": null, "upload_time": 1732379959}, "documentation": ["# GenStates\n\nGenStates is an implentation of state machine, with [genruler](https://github.com/Jeffrey04/genruler) as the rule engine.\n\n## Usage\n\n```\nfrom genstates import Machine\nimport yaml\n\nwith open('schema.yaml') as file_schema:\n    machine = Machine(yaml.safe_load(file_schema))\n```\n\n### Fetching states\n\n* Get initial state by `machine.initial`\n* Get any state by `machine.states[$key]` where `$key` is the key for the state\n\n### Fetching transitions\n\n* Get all possible transitions for a given `state` by\n  ```\n  transitions = machine.get_transitions(state)\n  ```\n* Get a specific transition for a given `state` by\n  ```\n  transition = machine.get_transition(state, transition_key)\n  ```\n\n### Progressing from one state to another\n\n* If you have a known transition, pass in a context dictionary that the rule understands\n  ```\n  transition.check_condition(context)\n  ```\n* If you are not sure about the destination, use `.progress()`\n  ```\n  destination_state = machine.progress(current_state, context)\n  ```\n  Note that if multiple transitions are possible it will result in an error\n\n## Schema\n\nAssuming you are storing the transition as a YAML\n\n```\nmachine:\n  initial_state: $initial_state\n\nstates:\n  $state_key: # can have many states\n    name: $state_name\n    transitions: # can have many transitions\n      $transition_key:\n        name: $transition_name\n        destination: $transition_destination\n        rule: $transition_rule\n```\n\nwhere:\n\n* `$initial_state`: a state key value, must be defined in the `states` section\n* `$state_key`: a unique key for the state\n* `state_name`: a descriptive name for the state\n* `$transition_key`:  a unique key for the transition\n* `$transition_destination`:  a state key value, must be defined in the states section, pointing back to the same state is allowed\n* `$transition_name`:  a descriptive name for the transition\n* `$transition_rule`:  a rule that has to return `True`"], "modules": [{"name": "genstates", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "genstates.logger", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "genstates.State", "bases": [], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "genstates.State.key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "genstates.State.name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "genstates.Transition", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "genstates.Transition.check_condition", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "context", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Always returns a boolean, regardless rule is valid for given context.\nIf rule is invalid, returns a False"]}], "class_variables": [{"name": "genstates.Transition.key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "genstates.Transition.name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "genstates.Transition.origin", "type": {"name": "State", "xref": {"fqname": "genstates.State", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "genstates.Transition.destination", "type": {"name": "State", "xref": {"fqname": "genstates.State", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "genstates.Transition.rule", "type": {"name": "Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "collections.abc.Callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "[dict[Any, Any]]", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "genstates.Machine", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "genstates.Machine.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "schema", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "genstates.Machine.graph", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Return a graphviz dot graph notation as string"]}, {"name": "genstates.Machine.get_transitions", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "state", "type": {"name": "State", "xref": {"fqname": "genstates.State", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "dict", 